General accessor function for RLum S4 class objects

Source: R/set_Risoe.BINfileData.R
set_Risoe.BINfileData.Rd

Function calls object-specific get functions for RisoeBINfileData S4 class objects.

set_Risoe.BINfileData(
  METADATA = data.frame(),
  DATA = list(),
  .RESERVED = list()
)

Arguments

METADATA

x

DATA

x

.RESERVED

x

Value

Return is the same as input objects as provided in the list.

Details

The function provides a generalised access point for specific Risoe.BINfileData objects.
Depending on the input object, the corresponding get function will be selected. Allowed arguments can be found in the documentations of the corresponding Risoe.BINfileData class.

Function version

0.1
